cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SI, cs.CY 

The paper proposes a machine learning-based framework for mobile air pollution sensing, which suggests that it could fall under the categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of urban big data to generate insights also suggests that it could fall under Information Retrieval (cs.IR) and Social and Information Networks (cs.SI). Finally, the focus on sustainable urban management suggests that it could also fall under Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
